V0419_01_00_00_0.text:
You look scared.
That's what I like!

V0419_01_00_00_1.text: You're like a tiny rabbit and I'm the apex predator!

V0419_01_00_01_0.text:
Let's do this!
No holds barred!

V0419_01_00_02_0.text:
Why do I have to Duel?
We both know how this is gonna end.

V0419_01_00_03_0.text:
You asked for it...
And you’re gonna get it!

V0419_01_00_04_0.text:
Yuma Tsukumo!
I've been lookin' forward to Dueling ya!

V0419_01_00_05_0.text:
I never show mercy!
Not even to my friends!
Let's go, Alito!

V0419_01_00_06_0.text:
I know only one Duelist who's this strong...
Mizar!

V0419_01_00_07_0.text:
You really want Barian vs Barian?
Your funeral!

V0419_01_00_08_0.text: I got a score to settle with ya, Vector!

V0419_01_00_09_0.text: You'll pay for everything you've done, Don Thousand!

V0419_03_00_01_0.text: Guess who gets to go now!?

V0419_03_00_04_0.text: Stop thinking you're a hotshot, punk!

V0419_03_00_05_0.text:
Wait a sec...
I'm in real trouble!

V0419_05_00_00_0.text: This is the draw that's gonna defeat you!

V0419_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0419_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0419_16_00_00_0.text:
This is the grand finale!
See ya later!

V0419_21_00_00_0.text:
C'mon!
Shouldn't you have surrendered by now?

V0419_21_00_04_0.text: You won't get away with those silly strategies for long!

V0419_21_00_05_0.text: How can I be so super-duper lame!?

V0419_28_00_01_0.text:
You never had a chance.
You were just too stubborn to quit.

V0419_28_00_02_0.text: If you want power, I'm the one who can give it to you.

V0419_28_00_02_1.text: Power enough to rule your whole pathetic planet!

V0419_28_00_03_0.text:
You've got talent.
I could use a creative guy like you.

V0419_29_00_00_0.text: I can't believe you countered every move I made...

V0419_29_00_01_0.text:
You got me today.
But tomorrow’s another day!

V0419_33_00_00_0.text: I thought of a good strategy!

V0419_30_00_02_0.text: I got a question for ya.

V0419_34_00_00_0.text: It sure would mean a lot if you sign this card for me.

V0419_34_00_01_0.text: I Set one bear and end my turn!

V0419_34_00_02_0.text: Remember - you agreed to lose this Duel on purpose.

V0419_34_00_03_0.text: Only a Sports Duel will cure your blues!

V0419_34_00_04_0.text: Work out your problems by working out!

V0419_34_00_05_0.text: This is bad! Am I a goner!?

V0419_34_00_06_0.text: It's over... I'm low-fiving the floor...

V0419_34_00_07_0.text: I always have the inside scoop!

V0419_34_00_09_0.text: Here's a direct attack... straight to your heart!

V0419_35_00_00_0.text: If power's what you want, I'm your new best friend!

V0419_35_00_01_0.text:
I'm Girag!
The brave warrior who's always ready for a fight!

V0419_36_00_01_0.text:
It's your turn.
Don't mess up!

V0419_36_00_08_0.text:
Remember, Yuma.
You don't gotta throw this Duel.

V0419_36_00_09_0.text: Yuma, how about taking this Duel seriously for a change...

V0419_36_00_10_0.text:
This is horrible...
I'm feelin' the low...

V0419_08_00_01_0.text: Witness the true power of the Barians!

V0419_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Barian Untopia!

V0419_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Seventh Ascension!

V0419_08_00_06_0.text: I'll toss this Rank-Up-Magic to activate Seventh Ascension!

V0419_08_00_06_1.text: It gains the same effect as that Rank-Up-Magic I tossed!

V0419_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Reload!

V0419_08_00_07_1.text: I return my hand to my deck and then draw the same amount!

V0419_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Jack-In-The-Hand!

V0419_08_00_08_1.text:
I'll let you have a card!
Choose!

V0419_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Kaminote Blow!

V0419_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rebirth of the Seventh Emperors!

V0419_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Reincarnation of the Seventh Emperors!

V0419_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Seventh Eternity!

V0419_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rocket Hand!

V0419_08_00_14_1.text: I equip this card on a monster!

V0419_08_00_15_0.text: The equipped Rocket Hand's effect activates!

V0419_08_00_15_1.text: By sending this card to the Graveyard, I can destroy a card!

V0419_08_00_16_0.text:
This'll come in handy!
I activate my Trap!
Memory Loss!

V0419_09_00_00_0.text: I activate Number 106: Giant Hand's effect!

V0419_09_00_02_0.text:
Giant Red Hand!
Activate your effect!

V0419_09_00_02_1.text: Use 1 Chaos Overlay Unit to negate all other face-up cards!

V0419_09_00_03_0.text: No matter what you try, Giant Red Hand will crush it!

V0419_09_00_05_0.text: When Ice Hand is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0419_09_00_05_1.text: It destroys a Spell or Trap and Special Summons Fire Hand!

V0419_09_00_06_0.text: When Fire Hand is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0419_09_00_06_1.text: It destroys your monster and Special Summons Ice Hand!

V0419_09_00_07_1.text: Get rid of the card you got and take damage!

V0419_09_00_08_1.text: I Special Summon this card and destroy one of your cards!

V0419_09_00_09_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Ronin Raccoon Sandayu's effect!

V0419_09_00_10_0.text: Baby Raccoon Tantan's effect activates when it's flipped!

V0419_09_00_10_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 2 Beast from my deck!

V0419_09_00_11_0.text: When Baby Raccoon Ponpoko is Summoned, its effect activates!

V0419_09_00_11_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 2 Beast from my deck in defense!

V0419_13_00_00_0.text:
Grrrr...
Crush the world in your mighty fist!

V0419_37_00_00_0.text: It has the power to harness this chaotic world!

V0419_37_00_00_1.text:
Its fist will smash the land!
Its fingers will tear the sky!

V0419_37_00_01_0.text: I have to give up my own strength to control this monster...

V0419_37_00_01_1.text:
But I'm willing to make that sacrifice!
Chaos Xyz Evolution!

V0419_13_00_03_0.text:
Set this Duel on fire!
Number 58: Burner Visor!

V0419_37_00_02_1.text: The wisdom to confuse the world!

V0419_13_00_12_0.text: I Special Summon a Kagemusha Raccoon Token!

V0419_19_00_17_0.text:
Chu-Ske the Mouse Fighter!
Strike 'em hard, little guy!
